  ('optometrist-moex-02384', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在光學系統中，單色光可以分成五種賽德爾像差（Seidel aberration），分別為①球面像差（spherical', '["彗星像差（coma）", "徑向散光（radial astigmatism）", "場曲（curvature of field） ⑤畸變（distortion）。在眼鏡鏡片的驗配選擇上，相對重要的是那三個？", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4fb1bcbf806b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7bd68f442a10", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
